OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784913524
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FThe UK has withdrawn remaining
OL,7,Fdiplomatic staff from Iran as the US
OL,8,Fcompleted its 12th consecutive night
OL,9,Fof strikes on the nation.
OL,11,FAnnouncing the withdrawal, a statement
OL,12,Ffrom the Foreign Office (FCDO) read:
OL,13,F"Due to the security situation, UK
OL,14,Fstaff have been temporarily withdrawn
OL,15,Ffrom Iran.
OL,17,F"Our embassy continues to operate
OL,18,Fremotely."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
