PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784913524
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FThe FCDO advises against all travel to
OL,7,FIran, saying British and dual British-
OL,8,FIranian residents face "significant
OL,9,Frisk of arrest, questioning or
OL,10,Fdetention".
OL,12,FA similar move was made in February
OL,13,Fahead of US and Israeli combat
OL,14,Foperations.
OL,16,FUS Central Command said late on
OL,17,FWednesday that the 12th night of
OL,18,Fattacks was designed to "further
OL,19,Fdegrade Iran's ability to threaten
OL,20,Fcivilian mariners and commercial
OL,21,Fvessels transiting regional waters".
OL,26,@pD@XOUrD@JO]zD@YOU}D@cO]
