OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784913524
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FThey said US forces struck military
OL,7,Ftargets including maritime
OL,8,Fcapabilities, missile and drone
OL,9,Fstorage facilities, coastal
OL,10,Fsurveillance sites and air defence
OL,11,Fassets.
OL,13,F"As of today, CentCom has redirected
OL,14,Fnine commercial vessels and disabled
OL,15,Fone to prevent ships from entering or
OL,16,Fdeparting Iranian ports," a statement
OL,17,Fread.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
