OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784913524
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,F"More than 50,000 US service members
OL,7,Fare operating across the Middle East
OL,8,Fand remain highly vigilant, focused,
OL,9,Flethal, and ready."
OL,11,FMissiles struck near the cities of
OL,12,FAhvaz, Ramshir and Andimeshk in
OL,13,Fwestern Iran, according to Iranian
OL,14,Fstate media, which said two people
OL,15,Fwere killed in the town of Shalamcheh
OL,16,Fon the Iraqi border.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
