OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784913524
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FKuwait's army said on X that the
OL,7,Fcountry's air defences were
OL,8,F"confronting attacks by hostile
OL,9,Fdrones, following the sinful Iranian
OL,10,Faggression".
OL,12,FUS President Donald Trump warned on
OL,13,FWednesday that one bridge or power
OL,14,Fplant would be destroyed for each ship
OL,15,Fshot at by Iran in the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@KO]
