CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784913524
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,F"From this point forward, any time the
OL,7,FIslamic Republic of Iran shoots at a
OL,8,Fship in the Strait of Hormuz, whether
OL,9,Fit be by Missile, Rocket, Drone, or
OL,10,Fany other device or weapon, the United
OL,11,FStates will bomb and destroy ONE
OL,12,FBRIDGE OR POWER PLANT, including those
OL,13,Flocated next to, or in, the Capital
OL,14,FCity of Tehran," Trump wrote on social
OL,15,Fmedia.
OL,17,FForeign minister Seyed Abbas Araghchi
OL,18,Falso said an "eye for an eye" approach
OL,19,Fwould be adopted by Iran.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@PO]zD@NOUzD@]O]
