OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784913524
OL,3,CUK withdraws diplomatic staff from
OL,4,CIran as US airstrikes continue
OL,6,FIran launched a missile attack on a
OL,7,FJordanian city while alerts were
OL,8,Fsounded in Bahrain and Saudi Arabia.
OL,10,FIran has responded to US attacks by
OL,11,Ftargeting energy infrastructure and
OL,12,Fdesalination plants which provide
OL,13,Fdrinking water in neighbouring Gulf
OL,14,Fcountries.
OL,16,FInternational law generally prohibits
OL,17,Fsuch attacks unless the infrastructure
OL,18,Fis being used for military purposes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
